caption:
✨ As we conclude #InternationalWellbeingMonth, we’re reflecting on how to create lasting changes in our daily routines. Here are a few simple yet impactful tips to enhance your overall wellbeing:

👩‍💻 Workspace Wellbeing: Evaluate your workspace setup. Small adjustments not only reduce physical strain, but also enhance productivity by improving your posture and comfort.

💪 Physical Wellbeing: Make it a habit to take regular breaks of 5-10 minutes every hour. The best breaks are those that allow you to move around and step away from screens.

🧠 Mental Wellbeing: Prioritize actual rest by blocking off time for vacations. Alternatively, consider learning a new skill or hobby that excites you. 

Tell us: what changes are you making to support your overall wellbeing?👂
